    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my reliable set of wheels, and it\u2019s looking for a new home. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super dependable for me\u2014perfect for someone who wants a smooth, worry-free ride without the brand-new price tag. The interior is nice and clean, and it drives like a dream! I'm sad to see it go, but I know you'll love it just as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you want to come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32500.0,
