    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously maintained and presents beautifully, striking the perfect balance between daily utility and premium feel. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss finish, accented by clean alloy wheels and only the minor stone chips one would expect from careful road use. Inside, the cabin is a smoke-free environment featuring supple leather upholstery with minimal bolster wear, and every electronic component\u2014from the dual-zone climate control to the infotainment system\u2014functions perfectly. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly with a documented history of regular synthetic oil changes and recent brake service. It drives straight and true, offering a quiet, composed ride that reflects its solid mechanical health. This is a dependable, turn-key car ready for its next owner to enjoy immediately.",
      "price": 34500.0,
