    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Hi there! \ud83d\udc4b I\u2019m parting ways with my reliable ride, and it's honestly such a gem. It\u2019s been well-loved and kept in great shape, so it's totally ready for all your upcoming adventures. Smooth handling, super comfortable, and it hasn't let me down once! If you're looking for a dependable car that still looks and feels fantastic, this is the one for you. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
