    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound driver\u2019s car powered by the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and double VANOS variable valve timing. The power is managed by a traditional 6-speed manual Getrag gearbox and a factory limited-slip differential. Crucially, the rear subframe has been reinforced to ensure chassis integrity under high torque loads. Suspension components have been maintained for precise turn-in, and the engine pulls cleanly to its 8,000 RPM redline with consistent compression across all cylinders. It presents in honest condition, showing minor aesthetic wear consistent with its mileage, but remains a performance-first machine with all major mechanical vulnerabilities addressed.",
